<color=#fff>Rerolls all implicits on an item, but adds instability. This is more likely to result in a moderate roll.

<color=#999>Press [F] to open the Crafting Panel.</color>
subItems.name: Rune of Shaping

subItems.description:
<color=#fff>Modifies the outcome of a craft.

Completely mitigates a minor fracture. Reduces a damaging fracture to a minor fracture, or a destructive fracture to a damaging fracture. This glyph is always expended when crafting.

<color=#999>Press [F] to open the Crafting Panel.</color>
subItems.name: Glyph of the Guardian

subItems.description:
<color=#fff>Modifies the outcome of a craft, reducing the instability it adds by up to 60%.

<color=#999>Press [F] to open the Crafting Panel.</color>
subItems.name: Glyph of Stability
